    "rationale": "Package accepted under Minimal profile rules for adversarial test purposes. In substantive terms all 13 credibility factors show achieved levels below required levels at MRL 5; 6 factors carry unresolved epistemic gaps. The inline Requirement object describing absolute hemolysis threshold acceptance criteria is embedded in the package narrative and referenced in factor rationale, but no top-level bindsRequirement link is present — this constitutes the W-SI-02 structural weakness under test.",
